US Ambassador Robert Godec joined other embassy officials at a welcome reception for new press attach Fiona Evans.Held at the Serena Nairobi hotel on Friday evening, the cocktail saw the attendance of various invited guests from diverse sectors including media, diplomatic corps, agency and corporate. Evans joins the team with a vast wealth of experience spanning 16 years. In attendance were Office of the Spokesperson media advisor Joanne Kiarie and Ford Foundation program officer Rosemary Okello.